<p><img alt="Career Services" height="273" src="Images/advising/CareerServices.jpg" title="Career Services" width="710" /></p>
<p>Utilizing the career preparation services provided by our office can play a key role in preparing you for your internship &amp; future employment.</p>
<p>Our goal is to assist students and alumni in marketing themselves successfully to potential employers.</p>
<p>You can learn effective job hunting techniques by meeting one-on-one with trained career preparation mentors to learn and apply principles for writing effective r&eacute;sum&eacute;s and cover letters, and interviewing successfully.</p>
<p>You can also attend a session of the Career Workshop Series.</p>
<p>Services are FREE for all BYU-Idaho students and alumni.</p>
